---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

const metadata = {
  title: 'How To Create Your Own Opportunities - Understanding Agency · The Second Design',
  description:
    "Open source release of The Second Design's How To Create Your Own Opportunities session on understanding agency - slide deck and participant workbook for educators and communities.",
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero ************************************* -->

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-28 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950">
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b
             from-slate-100 via-white to-slate-100
             dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-950 dark:to-violet-500/10"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="relative container max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase">
          Open Source Session
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">
          How To Create Your Own Opportunities
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          Understanding Agency
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          A session that helps learners recognize and develop their sense of agency - the belief that their actions matter and they can shape their own outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <a
          href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-300 px-3 py-1 hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition"
        >
          <Icon name="tabler:license" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" />
          CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
        </a>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-slate-900/5 dark:bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1">
          <Icon name="tabler:presentation" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" />
          Slide deck + workbook
        </span>
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-3 py-1"
        >
          <Icon name="tabler:users-group" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" />
          Designed for cohorts & workshops
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What the session does ************************ -->

  <section class="py-20 bg-white border-y border-slate-200
           dark:bg-slate-950/80 dark:border-slate-800">
    <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] items-start px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">
            Why this session exists
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Many learners feel like things just happen to them - that their circumstances, background, or luck determine their outcomes. This passive stance keeps them from taking initiative, making bold choices, or owning their path.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            This session helps people understand what agency really means, recognize where they already have it, and practice expanding it intentionally.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/80 p-5 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/70"
          >
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 mb-1.5">Core ideas it lands</h3>
            <ul class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 space-y-1.5">
              <li>• Agency is a skill, not a personality trait.</li>
              <li>• Small actions compound into real change.</li>
              <li>• You have more control than you think.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/80 p-5 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/70"
          >
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 mb-1.5">Where it works best</h3>
            <ul class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 space-y-1.5">
              <li>• Students starting new programs or transitions</li>
              <li>• Cohorts feeling stuck or passive</li>
              <li>• Anyone who needs to shift from "waiting" to "doing"</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick facts card -->
      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border bg-slate-50/80 border-slate-200 shadow-sm shadow-slate-200/80
               dark:bg-slate-900/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 dark:shadow-black/40 p-6 space-y-4"
      >
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 flex items-center gap-2">
          <Icon name="tabler:info-circle" class="w-4 h-4" />
          Session snapshot
        </h3>
        <dl class="space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
            <dt class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Format</dt>
            <dd class="text-right">Live session + reflection exercises</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
            <dt class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Length</dt>
            <dd class="text-right">~60–90 minutes (flexible)</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
            <dt class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Best for</dt>
            <dd class="text-right">Groups of 20–80 learners</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
            <dt class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Prerequisites</dt>
            <dd class="text-right">None - works for any stage</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Links to materials ********************************** -->

  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-3 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">
          Link to the materials
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          These files are ready to use as-is, but you're encouraged to adapt them to your learners and context.
          Translate, rearrange, add your own stories - just keep the attribution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Deck -->
        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1WWQyw2Ufq_-FbQofoCiQTq_nejilKzlaFc4cJ5-LVYw/copy"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group rounded-2xl border bg-white border-slate-200 shadow-sm shadow-slate-200/80
                 dark:bg-slate-900/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 dark:shadow-black/40
                 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between"
        >
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400"
            >
              <Icon name="tabler:presentation-analytics" class="w-4 h-4" />
              Slide deck
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">
              Facilitator slide deck (Google Slides)
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Slides for running the session end-to-end. Includes prompts, framing, and exercises for helping participants understand and develop their sense of agency.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
            Make a copy
            <Icon name="tabler:copy" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-y-0.5 transition-transform" />
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Workbook -->
        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/16Tu6aqMHe2E55PbLVrInjDFc0vWGpQwLhdE-8mMMRaI/copy"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group rounded-2xl border bg-white border-slate-200 shadow-sm shadow-slate-200/80
                 dark:bg-slate-900/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 dark:shadow-black/40
                 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between"
        >
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400"
            >
              <Icon name="tabler:notebook" class="w-4 h-4" />
              Workbook
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">
              Participant workbook (Google Doc)
            </h3>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Printable / digital workbook that guides learners through understanding agency, identifying where they have it, and making a plan to expand it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
            Make a copy
            <Icon name="tabler:copy" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-y-0.5 transition-transform" />
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- License / attribution ************************ -->

  <section class="py-20 bg-white border-t border-slate-200
           dark:bg-slate-950/90 dark:border-slate-800">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-sm md:text-base px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">
          How you're allowed to use this
        </h2>
        <a
          href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-xs font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-200 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition"
        >
          <img src="https://licensebuttons.net/l/by-nc-sa/4.0/80x15.png" alt="CC BY-NC-SA 4.0" class="h-4" />
          CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- You can -->
        <div class="space-y-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="tabler:circle-check" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" />
            You can
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Run this with your students, team, or community.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Adapt or translate it for your context.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Share improved versions under the same license.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- You cannot -->
        <div class="space-y-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="tabler:circle-x" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" />
            You cannot
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:x" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Sell this material.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:x" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Include it inside paid courses, paid cohorts, or commercial products.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:x" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Use it in programs where access is sold, without our written permission.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- You must -->
        <div class="space-y-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="tabler:pinned" class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500" />
            You must
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:pin" class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Credit <span class="font-semibold">The Second Design</span>.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:pin" class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Retain this license on shared adaptations.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="tabler:pin" class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span>Link back to the original source.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
        This work is licensed under a <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-300">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License</a>.
        For commercial licensing or institutional partnerships, reach out via the <a href="/contact" class="underline hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-300">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
